        <section class="- topic/section ">
            <title class="- topic/title ">Overview</title>
            <p class="- topic/p ">
                This release of the NXTCG platform introduces core marketplace functionality,
                allowing users to buy, sell, and manage NextGen trading cards through a fully
                integrated frontend and backend experience. The release focuses on establishing
                the end-to-end purchase flow, product configuration, user profile management,
                and platform stability.
            </p>
        </section>
        
        <section class="- topic/section ">
            <title class="- topic/title ">What’s New</title>
            
            <p class="- topic/p ">
                NXTCG now supports a complete trading card marketplace experience. Users can
                browse available cards, configure product attributes, add customized items to
                their cart, and securely complete checkout. Sellers can list cards for sale and
                manage their inventory directly from their user profile. The platform also
                introduces a modern storefront interface, navigation components, and landing
                pages to support discovery and usability.
            </p>
            
